{"tid":1489022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有片］景林邨厚德連儂隧道斬人","createTime":"2019-08-19T18:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T19:44:29.000Z","uid":65210,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb58951ab10ceb656ebe09c9373bb403cfc9e89e","tid":1489022,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"凌晨1時許，位於景林邨與厚德邨行人隧道內連儂牆，有手持利刀大漢掩至施襲，在場3人走避不及中刀被斬傷，兇徒傷人後逃去，其中一名女傷者手及背部中刀清醒，傷勢較重，由救護員送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救，另外兩人送將軍澳醫院。警方封鎖現場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場指行兇者約40-50歲，約高160cm，有一隻腳行動不便，大陸口音，身穿深藍色褲，淺藍色衫，黑鞋，戴有玉珠，最後出現位置為廣明苑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lB7PunEz3oY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlB7PunEz3oY&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=f329b4f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lB7PunEz3oY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/023206_b89d6dc29d00b8cf12d3c38fb02c4463.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F023206_b89d6dc29d00b8cf12d3c38fb02c4463.jpeg&h=55866fc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a07b326bcb904ced18fdf2e12798cf9842864d64","tid":1489022,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a1fdbde5b6f1e71a2657d271cb4dcea1187e09b","tid":1489022,"uid":65210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:34:45.000Z","msg":"整連儂牆都要放哨<br />\n唔好單獨行動<br />\n起碼要有朋友幫手睇水<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Stay alert!!! </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"07699975aa0b2c58e5f085139cf3c15b4332790f","tid":1489022,"uid":12462,"l